      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The exterior shows visible wear including some scratches and minor dents, with slight paint fading in areas. The interior has noticeable wear on the seats and surfaces, though it remains functional. The mechanical systems are operational but may benefit from some attention. Suitable for a buyer looking for basic reliable transportation at a reasonable price.",
